155
00:11:21,260 --> 00:11:24,520
Conflicts often occur at Indulgence House. I need to know a few skills.

156
00:11:24,520 --> 00:11:27,210
Otherwise, the beautiful ladies of the house will get bullied by those shameless men

157
00:11:27,210 --> 00:11:30,940
