167
00:12:02,840 --> 00:12:06,600
You do look a mess, but at least your face is intact.

168
00:12:06,600 --> 00:12:10,700
Although Young Master Liu is discourteous, he's quite hilarious.

169
00:12:11,420 --> 00:12:14,900
Do you really trust him? I don't!

170
00:12:14,900 --> 00:12:18,280
