171
00:12:18,280 --> 00:12:20,420
He's the perfect man. So is he paying for his misdeeds by protecting the girls here?

172
00:12:20,420 --> 00:12:22,420
I don't trust him.

173
00:12:22,420 --> 00:12:26,140
