177
00:13:17,720 --> 00:13:20,053
And they even stock  a wide variety of drugs?

178
00:13:20,053 --> 00:13:22,040
This doesn't look normal.

179
00:13:37,940 --> 00:13:40,060
Why are you in the apothecary?

180
00:13:40,060 --> 00:13:41,680
Are you sick?

181
00:13:45,680 --> 00:13:47,860
Sweet flags?

182
00:13:48,800 --> 00:13:50,640
You know the name of this herb?

183
00:13:57,480 --> 00:14:00,340
Young Masters, what's going on here?

184
00:14:00,340 --> 00:14:04,560
Nothing much. They're hungry and just asked me to stir fry some sweet flags for them.

185
00:14:14,920 --> 00:14:18,420
Sweet flag is a unique herb found only on Zhucui Mountain.

186
00:14:18,420 --> 00:14:21,280
It has a crispy texture and tastes refreshing. It's a perfect dish for cooling down in the heat.

187
00:14:21,280 --> 00:14:23,080
Most people in town pair it with wine.

188
00:14:23,080 --> 00:14:24,960
