189
00:14:24,960 --> 00:14:26,460
Try some.

190
00:14:29,960 --> 00:14:33,420
It seems like you hate beating around the bush, so I'll cut to the chase.

191
00:14:33,420 --> 00:14:37,440
If it is a food ingredient, why did you keep it with the other medicinal herbs?

192
00:14:37,440 --> 00:14:42,540
Also, it's my first time seeing an apothecary in a dance hall.

193
00:14:43,820 --> 00:14:45,880
You're no doubt from the same circle.

194
00:14:45,880 --> 00:14:48,560
You don't trust people easily.

195
00:14:48,560 --> 00:14:50,260
The ladies in the house spend most of their time dancing.

196
00:14:50,260 --> 00:14:52,820
They'll certainly get a few wounds here and there.

197
00:14:52,820 --> 00:14:59,480
Moreover, if there are patrons who intend to drug them, it's better for us to prepare the cure in-house.

198
00:14:59,480 --> 00:15:02,800
Sweet flags is also used as medicine to eliminate phlegm and cure chest stuffiness.

199
00:15:02,800 --> 00:15:05,320
You've only spoken about the use of sweet flags as a medicine.

200
00:15:05,320 --> 00:15:08,060
Do you know any other ways of using it?

201
00:15:17,020 --> 00:15:21,440
Did you run into anyone from Shenxiao Palace?

202
00:15:23,560 --> 00:15:26,160
There are only two ways to use sweet flags.

203
00:15:26,160 --> 00:15:29,620
You either use it to eliminate phlegm and cure chest stuffiness, or use it as a sedative.

204
00:15:29,620 --> 00:15:33,840
The people of Shenxiao Palace are the only ones who know how to make the sedative.

205
00:15:33,840 --> 00:15:37,640
Do you know anything else about Shenxiao Palace?

206
00:15:38,720 --> 00:15:40,840
Shenxiao Palace is extremely secretive.

207
00:15:40,840 --> 00:15:44,120
I've lived in Indulgence House for a long time, and I've certainly heard a thing or two about them.

208
00:15:44,120 --> 00:15:48,820
