209
00:15:48,820 --> 00:15:52,280
I heard that Truth Duster is a divine tool.

210
00:15:52,280 --> 00:15:57,640
In the hands of someone who doesn't know how to use it, it becomes nothing more than a normal duster.

211
00:15:57,640 --> 00:16:01,280
- Young Master Tang, are you— 
 - Young Master Liu.

212
00:16:02,700 --> 00:16:05,200
