213
00:16:05,200 --> 00:16:06,780
That's all we can say.

214
00:16:06,780 --> 00:16:08,880
We kindly ask for your understanding.

215
00:16:08,880 --> 00:16:10,420
Understood.

216
00:16:10,420 --> 00:16:11,860
Relationships between clans are really complex.

217
00:16:11,860 --> 00:16:13,820
I also don't want to interfere in other people's business.

218
00:16:13,820 --> 00:16:17,590
However, since fate brought us together, let me remind you of this.

219
00:16:17,590 --> 00:16:20,580
If I'm not mistaken, you were targeted by the members of Shenxiao Palace

220
00:16:20,580 --> 00:16:22,760
the moment you set foot in Zhucui Town.

221
00:16:22,760 --> 00:16:25,240
There's no need to keep looking for clues.

222
00:16:25,240 --> 00:16:29,100
If what the palace master wants is Truth Duster, he'll approach you sooner or later.

223
00:16:29,100 --> 00:16:31,540
Make sure you're prepared to face him by then.

224
00:16:34,260 --> 00:16:39,140
It seems I'll have to enjoy this plate of sweet flags by myself.

225
00:16:46,600 --> 00:16:48,540
Is he a friend or an enemy?

226
00:16:48,540 --> 00:16:51,140
I'm so confused.

227
00:16:52,520 --> 00:16:54,710
This place is a mixed bag.

228
00:16:54,710 --> 00:16:59,580
If we stay here a few more days, we might  learn more about Shenxiao Palace.

229
00:16:59,580 --> 00:17:03,500
Even if they do find us here, we'll be ready to face them by then.

230
00:17:07,860 --> 00:17:10,610
This is a nice and picturesque place.

231
00:17:10,610 --> 00:17:14,080
It has all of the Six Senses of the Mortal Realm that affect the eyes, ears, nose, tongue, body, and mind.

232
00:17:14,080 --> 00:17:15,160
You can find all of them here.

233
00:17:15,160 --> 00:17:19,850
If we stay here a few more days, not only can we find clues, but we can also gain some life experiences.

234
00:17:19,850 --> 00:17:21,710
I'm totally up for it!

235
00:17:21,710 --> 00:17:24,600
Liu Weiyang knows Shenxiao Palace very well.

236
00:17:24,600 --> 00:17:27,630
However, his answers were really vague when he was asked crucial questions.

237
00:17:27,630 --> 00:17:30,540
I'm worried that he was trying to learn more about us.

238
00:17:30,540 --> 00:17:34,920
That's not necessarily true. It could be the other way around.

239
00:17:34,920 --> 00:17:39,710
You mentioned those men of the Shenxiao Palace have a three-petal plus blossom tattoo.

